data.description: Price improvement - More than $100K below appraised value! Absolutely gorgeous ranch style home, 3br/2ba/5 car garage, formal dining rm, 2153 sqft home boasts an open floor plan w/rock fireplace, wood & tile floors, granite counter tops, induction cook-top, built-in convection oven & custom plantation shutters throughout. Large owner's suite w/multiple closets & bathroom w/separate vanities, jetted tub and large shower. A great opportunity to relax w/spectacular views while in your 2022 pool & spa! Private electric entrance gate on 14.36 acres for horses, cattle, livestock or just a place w/plenty of land for a family to settle down. Comes w/40'x80' pole barn, 20'x40' run shelter, 11'x'11 equipment shelter. A true feeling of being in the country on your own, yet less than 20 min from JBSA-Randolph & 25 min from all the convenience San Antonio has to offer. Definitely a MUST see to appreciate!
